### `.gitignore`

The `.gitignore` file ensures that sensitive or unnecessary files are excluded from version control. Here's a suitable `.gitignore` for this project:

```plaintext
# Ignore Python compiled files
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Ignore environment files
.env

# Ignore log files
*.log

# Ignore backup archives
/backup/

# Ignore IDE-specific files
.vscode/
.idea/

# Ignore OS-specific files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Ignore virtual environments
venv/
ENV/
env/